{
 "name": "RPlog_Into_the_Fray",
 "title": "Into the Fray",
 "summary": "During an Imperial civil war over the New Imperium, the loyalist Neo-Imperial fleet under Krieg and Captain Jal'Dana Rall aboard the Inquisitor moves to crush a traitor faction, only for New Republic's Ghost Squadron -- led by Kyrin with pilots Lance Corbet (Wildman) and Raxis -- to arrive and investigate. As Krieg recognizes his old enemy Kyrin, a swirling capital-ship and starfighter battle erupts: Dante and Liza Molokai lead the Alpha interceptors, Keline commands the Ravager against enemy corvettes, and the Ghosts engage the rogue Imperials. A fresh wave of eight heavy cruisers then drops out of hyperspace behind the task force, turning the engagement into a desperate, multi-sided melee with mounting losses on every side.",
